<section class="py-24 bg-surface-dark border-t-0 border-b border-border-dark relative">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mb-16 text-center lg:text-left relative">
      <span class="text-primary font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-3 block">Diagnóstico</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white font-display mb-4">
        El problema de la mayoría <br /> de las landings
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-dim text-lg max-w-2xl font-light">
        Por qué tu web actual podría estar costándote clientes todos los días.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <div class="group bg-background-dark border border-border-dark p-8 hover:border-white transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden rounded-sm hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="mb-6 bg-surface-dark w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-border-dark group-hover:border-primary group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl text-text-light group-hover:text-primary">timer_off</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Lentitud extrema</h3>
        <p class="text-text-dim text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Tus clientes no esperan. Si tu web tarda más de 3 segundos en cargar, el 53% se irá a la competencia antes de leer una palabra.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="group bg-background-dark border border-border-dark p-8 hover:border-white transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden rounded-sm hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="mb-6 bg-surface-dark w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-border-dark group-hover:border-primary group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl text-text-light group-hover:text-primary">visibility_off</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Diseño genérico</h3>
        <p class="text-text-dim text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Plantillas de Wordpress que "se ven bonitas" pero no transmiten autoridad ni diferencian tu marca personal del resto.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="group bg-background-dark border border-border-dark p-8 hover:border-white transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden rounded-sm hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="mb-6 bg-surface-dark w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-border-dark group-hover:border-primary group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl text-text-light group-hover:text-primary">psychology_alt</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Mensaje confuso</h3>
        <p class="text-text-dim text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Textos que hablan de ti ("somos líderes") en lugar de hablarle a los problemas y deseos de tu cliente ideal.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="group bg-background-dark border border-border-dark p-8 hover:border-white transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden rounded-sm hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="mb-6 bg-surface-dark w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-border-dark group-hover:border-primary group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl text-text-light group-hover:text-primary">savings</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Bajo retorno (ROI)</h3>
        <p class="text-text-dim text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Inviertes en anuncios de Facebook o Google, pero el tráfico llega a un "colador" donde pierdes el 90% de las oportunidades.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
